before,

322
00:14:37,585 --> 00:14:39,462
and it could happen again.

323
00:14:39,462 --> 00:14:42,381
All I'm saying is,
we've got to stay sharp.

324
00:14:45,343 --> 00:14:47,178
[engine revving]

325
00:14:47,178 --> 00:14:49,347
‐ I hate to say it,
President Yagiri,

326
00:14:49,347 --> 00:14:51,432
but things are kind of bad
for you.

327
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:53,434
